list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Removed a very annoying redundant "error:" tag that was appearing in messages. This would lead to error messages like
error: error: invalid grant.
Not the polished prose we all strive for in error messages.

Preparing to update some internal bookkeeping. Best to commit before any substantial changes happen. This also inlcudes automated ersatz client and token exchange tests.

Mostly this was converting using various old constructors for tokens to using centralized factory methods and the fall out from that. This removed a ton of repetitive cruft from the project.

All tests pass so this phase of the refactoring is finally over.
